  "runtimeRules": [
    "ListEndpoints supports no filters, no pagination, and no client-provided sorting.",
    "Backend normalizes unknown or missing parameter location to Query when creating/updating endpoint.",
    "Backend auto-creates missing Path parameters from placeholders in path and forces Path parameters to IsRequired=true.",
    "CreateEndpoint consumes endpoint subscription quota. UpdateEndpoint does not re-consume quota.",
    "UpdateEndpoint replaces all existing parameters and responses with the new request payload in one transaction.",
    "DeleteEndpoint relies on DB cascade delete for children.",
    "GetEndpointDetail resolves URL using DefaultValue first, then Examples[0].",
    "GetResolvedUrl reads raw query string pairs and only uses values matching path parameter names.",
    "GetResolvedUrl precedence is explicit query value > DefaultValue > Examples[0].",
    "GetResolvedUrl can return isFullyResolved=false and resolvedUrl=null when one or more path params are missing.",
    "GetPathParamMutations returns zero mutations when endpoint has no Path parameters.",
    "Mutation types are dynamic by dataType and format. FE must not hardcode a single fixed mutation list."
  ],
